Part A
1 Implementing three nodes point to point network with duplex links
between them.

2 Implementing transmission of ping messages /trace router over a
network topology consisting of 6 nodes.

3 Implementing an Ethernet LAN using n nodes and setting multiple
traffic nodes and plotting congestion window for different
source/destination.

4 Implementing simple ESS and with transmitting nodes in wireless
LAN by simulation.

5 Implementing and studying performance of GSM on NS2/NS3 or a
equivalent environment.

6 Implementing and studying the performance of CDMA on NS2/NS3 or
equivalent Environment.


Part B

7 Program for detecting code using CRC-CCITT. 

8 Program to find the shortest path between vertices using bellman-ford
algorithm.

9 Using TCP/IP sockets ,client-server program to make the client to send
the file name and to make the server send back the contents of
requested file if present.

10 Program on datagram socket for client/server to display the messages
on client side,typed at the server side.

11 Program for simple RSA algorithm to encrypt and decrypt the data. 

12 Program for congestion control using leaky bucket algorithm. 
